description:
The CSC Jackpot is a digital lottery style game based on blockchain technology that ensures fairness of the draw and absolute transparency of the result.

A transparent prize fund that is based on ticket sales and a fair draw process that can be verified by the user on the CSC Jakcpot website make this the safest and most secure way to win!

There is a lot to play for with exciting cash prizes each day and a monthly jackpot!
name: CSC JACKPOT
